So, there is where people do not understand
and they do not come back and then they get

00:38:27.670 --> 00:38:28.670
lost.

00:38:28.670 --> 00:38:32.630
Next program I come in, they said, "Mother
you cured me.

00:38:32.630 --> 00:38:40.719
All right, of this thing I was cured, but
now I have got this problem."

00:38:40.719 --> 00:38:47.930
So, all My life I'm curing them and all My
time is wasted like that.

00:38:47.930 --> 00:38:52.630
So best thing is that you become the doctor;
you become everything.

00:38:52.630 --> 00:38:54.859
Why don't you become?

00:38:54.859 --> 00:39:00.160
You all can become that; you all have that
power.

00:39:00.160 --> 00:39:02.950
So you get it.

00:39:02.950 --> 00:39:05.400
So you don't have to do anything just now.

00:39:05.400 --> 00:39:14.390
You all have to ... I'll just tell you how
we are going to nourish our centers and we

00:39:14.390 --> 00:39:17.089
are going to get our Realization.

00:39:17.089 --> 00:39:24.650
I am very happy to know that you are anxious
to do something about it.

00:39:24.650 --> 00:39:27.239
May God bless you!

00:39:27.239 --> 00:39:30.479
Nice to see such people!

00:39:30.479 --> 00:39:39.809
Question: For somebody who is not here and
who is really sick, can You help them?

00:39:39.809 --> 00:39:47.279
Shri Mataji: I can, but main thing is, you
see, that such a person you can help him.

00:39:47.279 --> 00:39:48.789
First of all, you get all right.

00:39:48.789 --> 00:39:57.029
You know all about it and then you can go
and help that person, because the best thing

00:39:57.029 --> 00:40:01.009
is that your knowledge will improve as you
help that person, gradually.

00:40:01.009 --> 00:40:04.069
It's very practical, and it all helps.

00:40:04.069 --> 00:40:05.069
All right?

00:40:05.069 --> 00:40:10.359
Question: You talk about our habits and weakness
and how to overcome that.

00:40:10.359 --> 00:40:14.119
Can You talk a little bit more about it?

00:40:14.119 --> 00:40:19.249
Shri Mataji: See, we are weak because we are
ignorant first of all.

00:40:19.249 --> 00:40:26.089
As I told you, we are holding the snake and
there's darkness and in that darkness we don't

00:40:26.089 --> 00:40:41.499
see that this is going to bite us.

00:40:41.499 --> 00:41:02.069
But, when you become enlightened, you become
a very powerful, dynamic person, absolutely.

00:41:02.069 --> 00:41:05.599
And you separate yourself from your habits.

00:41:05.599 --> 00:41:08.109
You see it very clearly.

00:41:08.109 --> 00:41:13.219
Then you don't talk that "I have this habit
or that habit."

00:41:13.219 --> 00:41:15.239
You don't say like that.

00:41:15.239 --> 00:41:22.660
Like a person would come and say, "Mother,
you know, my Agnya is catching; this chakra

00:41:22.660 --> 00:41:23.660
is catching.

00:41:23.660 --> 00:41:26.670
That means I have too much ego."

00:41:26.670 --> 00:41:29.969
But they don't say, "I have ego."

00:41:29.969 --> 00:41:37.039
I mean if you tell somebody, "You have ego,"
they'll hit you hard, isn't it?

00:41:37.039 --> 00:41:39.930
But if a person gets it, he feels it.

00:41:39.930 --> 00:41:45.849
And he says, "Mother, I have too much problem
with the Agnya Chakra so please clear it up."

00:41:45.849 --> 00:41:50.779
So, if you have any habits - say supposing
there are people who used to take drugs.

00:41:50.779 --> 00:41:58.369
In the beginning I had horrible people in
England, about seven of them, all drug addicts

00:41:58.369 --> 00:41:59.650
and things.

00:41:59.650 --> 00:42:07.339
Of course, very well-educated, professors
and things, but all drug addicts, hippies

00:42:07.339 --> 00:42:09.910
and violent people, really.

00:42:09.910 --> 00:42:15.339
When they came to Me, it was not easy to handle
them.

00:42:15.339 --> 00:42:20.549
But they are today the foundation of Sahaja
Yoga.

00:42:20.549 --> 00:42:22.869
Wonderful people they are.

00:42:22.869 --> 00:42:30.430
Now what happened, they said, "We want to
get rid of it but we can't.

00:42:30.430 --> 00:42:33.609
We just can't help it."

00:42:33.609 --> 00:42:39.559
But you will be amazed, overnight they gave
up, overnight.

00:42:39.559 --> 00:42:44.640
Just it happens because you see the light
and you throw the snake, just happens.

00:42:44.640 --> 00:42:46.099
You don't have to think about it, just happens.

00:42:46.099 --> 00:43:02.279
I never tell them these Ten Commandments - don't
do this, don't do that.

00:43:02.279 --> 00:43:09.630
Don't tell them.

00:43:09.630 --> 00:43:13.039
Just it works from within.

00:43:13.039 --> 00:43:16.769
Why should I tell them?

00:43:16.769 --> 00:43:20.380
Why should I give them a lecture?

00:43:20.380 --> 00:43:21.380
There's no need.

00:43:21.380 --> 00:43:29.069
They themselves become their own master and
the mastery is that the master cures and gives

00:43:29.069 --> 00:43:30.069
you powers.

00:43:30.069 --> 00:43:32.579
You develop that dignity; it's remarkable
what happens.

00:43:32.579 --> 00:43:35.839
To Me, it's not a surprise because I know
what you are.

00:43:35.839 --> 00:43:36.839
You are so glorious.

00:43:36.839 --> 00:43:38.880
It's like you take a small little, say a television
to a remote corner of India and in some village

00:43:38.880 --> 00:43:44.390
and show them and say that "Here is a place,
this box will show you all the kinds of music

00:43:44.390 --> 00:43:46.539
and all kinds of dramas and this."

00:43:46.539 --> 00:43:47.539
They say, "What?

00:43:47.539 --> 00:43:48.539
This box?

00:43:48.539 --> 00:43:49.579
How is it going to work out?"

00:43:49.579 --> 00:43:55.390
And, you put it to the mains and it starts
working and they say, "It's fantastic."

00:43:55.390 --> 00:43:56.390
It's like that.

00:43:56.390 --> 00:43:59.069
We are fantastic, we are glorious but we have
yet to be connected, that's all.

00:43:59.069 --> 00:44:04.829
It just happens, you don't have to force yourself,
you don't have to do anything.

00:44:04.829 --> 00:44:05.940
It just works.

00:44:05.940 --> 00:44:08.150
The inner force works it out.

00:44:08.150 --> 00:44:09.150
Anything else?

00:44:09.150 --> 00:44:12.579
Such nice people have come today, I am very
happy.

00:44:12.579 --> 00:44:13.990
They are asking such nice questions.

00:44:13.990 --> 00:44:14.990
[Applause]

00:44:14.990 --> 00:44:15.990
Really, wonderful!

00:44:15.990 --> 00:44:18.420
But you must promise that you all will prosper
in a proper way and work it out because it's

00:44:18.420 --> 00:44:19.839
a waste then I feel.

00:44:19.839 --> 00:44:25.440
You know I was so enamored by the Russians
and the Eastern Bloc people because not that

00:44:25.440 --> 00:44:32.430
they only come to My lecture, not that they
only listen to Me, but they work it out.

00:44:32.430 --> 00:44:35.869
And they are moving everywhere.

00:44:35.869 --> 00:44:41.450
Now people have moved to Siberia and all these
far-fetched places.

00:44:41.450 --> 00:44:45.900
They have taken the whole map.

00:44:45.900 --> 00:44:55.569
They brought the whole map before Me and said,
"Mother, now tell us where should we go."

00:44:55.569 --> 00:44:58.069
They have gone all out.

00:44:58.069 --> 00:44:59.710
So must understand the importance of it.

00:44:59.710 --> 00:45:03.039
It's not just like going to one lecture or
to another lecture.

00:45:03.039 --> 00:45:09.950
This is one thing you have to promise in your
heart that "Mother, we'll all become great

00:45:09.950 --> 00:45:10.950
trees."

00:45:10.950 --> 00:45:13.499
You have such great trees here.

00:45:13.499 --> 00:45:17.059
God has created such beautiful thing here.

00:45:17.059 --> 00:45:23.160
Why not in Canada we should have some great
personalities, great saints?

00:45:23.160 --> 00:45:25.200
Now, any other question?

00:45:25.200 --> 00:45:32.309
Question: In order to develop realization,
if you're not living somewhere close to where

00:45:32.309 --> 00:45:35.619
there is a center then what do we do?

00:45:35.619 --> 00:45:38.900
Shri Mataji: There's no need to depend on
Me.

00:45:38.900 --> 00:45:45.200
We have people here who are experts, who have
really become masters.

00:45:45.200 --> 00:45:48.039
And, they will definitely help you so it doesn't
matter.

00:45:48.039 --> 00:45:49.470
I am always with you.

00:45:49.470 --> 00:45:54.900
Whenever you think of Me, you'll know I am
with you and you can always write to Me.

00:45:54.900 --> 00:46:00.290
There's nothing to feel that I'm away from
you, that ... maybe that is the reason people

00:46:00.290 --> 00:46:02.079
don't go further with it.

00:46:02.079 --> 00:46:04.569
But as you trust Me, you trust yourself.

00:46:04.569 --> 00:46:05.789
You must trust yourself.

00:46:05.789 --> 00:46:09.420
You must have faith in yourself that you are
quite capable and you can do it.

00:46:09.420 --> 00:46:14.319
You can do it and that there are people who
will help you.

00:46:14.319 --> 00:46:18.319
They are very humble, sweet, beautiful people.

00:46:18.319 --> 00:46:23.150
You will like them and they'll all help you
till you become perfect.

00:46:23.150 --> 00:46:25.150
Such love, I tell you.

00:46:25.150 --> 00:46:26.749
Same thing [someone interrupts].

00:46:26.749 --> 00:46:27.749
Children?

00:46:27.749 --> 00:46:29.619
Children are the best, children are the best
for Sahaja Yoga.

00:46:29.619 --> 00:46:31.650
They take to Sahaja Yoga in no time.

00:46:31.650 --> 00:46:37.599
Most of the children these days are born realized
and we have to just understand them.

00:46:37.599 --> 00:46:41.269
So many children are born realized.

00:46:41.269 --> 00:46:50.569
Children are the best to understand Sahaja
Yoga, to work it out and they just of a very

00:46:50.569 --> 00:46:53.319
high level, I should say.

00:46:53.319 --> 00:47:07.140
Like the other day there was a child who was
receiving a phone.

00:47:07.140 --> 00:47:27.210
He said, "Oh, it's all right.

00:47:27.210 --> 00:47:39.299
You are not a yogi."

00:47:39.299 --> 00:47:46.529
Puts it down the phone.

00:47:46.529 --> 00:47:53.749
So I said, "How do you know?"

00:47:53.749 --> 00:47:56.130
"Mother, he had no vibrations.

00:47:56.130 --> 00:47:57.859
How could I know?

00:47:57.859 --> 00:48:00.459
Why should I talk to him?

00:48:00.459 --> 00:48:03.920
Let it be, I put down the phone."

00:48:03.920 --> 00:48:08.000
Question: Mother, is it a symbol of Your photograph
that gives vibrations?

00:48:08.000 --> 00:48:11.349
The willpower [can't understand the rest of
the question]

00:48:11.349 --> 00:48:12.999
Shri Mataji: It's true.

00:48:12.999 --> 00:48:17.849
My photograph luckily has some sort of a coefficience
that it emits vibrations.

00:48:17.849 --> 00:48:24.509
I mean, I would like anybody else's photograph
if it does, because it's a good idea; but

00:48:24.509 --> 00:48:30.180
I don't think there's anyone like that, because
none of the incarnations and none of the saints

00:48:30.180 --> 00:48:31.180
were photographed.

00:48:31.180 --> 00:48:32.249
It's very surprising, nobody was photographed.

00:48:32.249 --> 00:48:38.309
At the most, and also, nobody was portrayed
in their lifetime, because you know what happened

00:48:38.309 --> 00:48:41.329
to all the saints and to all the incarnations:
when they lived, everybody was after their

00:48:41.329 --> 00:48:42.329
lives.

00:48:42.329 --> 00:48:43.329
No question of having so many people.

00:48:43.329 --> 00:48:46.549
I mean, even Christ had hardly twelve people
and how they tortured His life!

00:48:46.549 --> 00:48:56.089
Actually, if you see His public life, He lived
hardly for three and a half years and they

00:48:56.089 --> 00:48:57.119
crucified Him.

00:48:57.119 --> 00:49:00.729
So, this is what the world was.

00:49:00.729 --> 00:49:03.309
It's not so bad now.

00:49:03.309 --> 00:49:10.519
I mean, nobody is going to crucify Me, but
still there were no photographs.

00:49:10.519 --> 00:49:16.579
So, the modern times has another advantage
that they have photographs, and they will

00:49:16.579 --> 00:49:21.789
show you lots of beautiful photographs and
things which will stun you.

00:49:21.789 --> 00:49:25.709
But that will be later on, you can see.

00:49:25.709 --> 00:49:30.219
But even this is such an advantage that I
can talk to so many people.

00:49:30.219 --> 00:49:47.829
And aeroplane is such an advantage that I
can travel all over the world.

00:49:47.829 --> 00:50:03.849
Everything is such an advantage today.

00:50:03.849 --> 00:50:10.949
The communication have improved so much that
I could come to Canada.

00:50:10.949 --> 00:50:12.449
Can you imagine Christ coming to Canada?

00:50:12.449 --> 00:50:13.449
[Laughter]

00:50:13.449 --> 00:50:17.609
So, I mean, see the whole advantage is there
and in Russia I have given realization to

00:50:17.609 --> 00:50:19.279
people on television, on television.

00:50:19.279 --> 00:50:21.950
But they are extremely sensitive people, extremely
sensitive.

00:50:21.950 --> 00:50:28.819
I mean, in the program when we had the scientists,
one of the scientist got up and said, "But

00:50:28.819 --> 00:50:35.279
Mother, please tell us how You cure people
when they only attend Your program when they

00:50:35.279 --> 00:50:36.489
are so many."

00:50:36.489 --> 00:50:40.109
I said, "I don't know if I've cure people."

00:50:40.109 --> 00:50:42.130
But they are so sensitive.

00:50:42.130 --> 00:50:44.150
Their spirituality is just there.

00:50:44.150 --> 00:50:45.759
It touches so fast.

00:50:45.759 --> 00:50:49.069
We can say that they are very, very ultra-modern
sensitive instruments.

00:50:49.069 --> 00:50:50.650
Just touch them and it works.

00:50:50.650 --> 00:50:51.650
It's rather surprising.

00:50:51.650 --> 00:50:53.079
Their attention is so good.

00:50:53.079 --> 00:50:55.390
Their attention is so good.

00:50:55.390 --> 00:50:58.619
So, that's what it is, it works.

00:50:58.619 --> 00:51:03.229
But if they can get it, you can get it.

00:51:03.229 --> 00:51:05.079
You can do it.

00:51:05.079 --> 00:51:07.099
But also, another problem in the West is that
we are very guilty people.

00:51:07.099 --> 00:51:10.920
For nothing at all, we are extremely - one
side we are destroying ourselves, that's one

00:51:10.920 --> 00:51:16.609
way and another is all the time we feel, 'I've
done this wrong.

00:51:16.609 --> 00:51:17.900
I've done that wrong.

00:51:17.900 --> 00:51:18.940
Sorry, Sorry!'

00:51:18.940 --> 00:51:20.559
English language is full of it.

00:51:20.559 --> 00:51:21.849
So, we all the time start feeling sorry.

00:51:21.849 --> 00:51:25.549
There's no need to feel all that guilt and
sin and all this nonsensical ideas.

00:51:25.549 --> 00:51:28.410
That really spoils the game for Me also.

00:51:28.410 --> 00:51:31.819
I have seen Americans are the worst.

00:51:31.819 --> 00:51:40.900
They are guilty for this and guilty for that.

00:51:40.900 --> 00:51:44.219
What is there to be guilty?

00:51:44.219 --> 00:51:52.079
After all, you are human beings and if you
have done any mistakes, doesn't matter.

00:51:52.079 --> 00:51:54.039
After all you're not Gods.

00:51:54.039 --> 00:51:55.039
So what?

00:51:55.039 --> 00:51:58.359
If you have done mistakes, all right forget
it.

00:51:58.359 --> 00:51:59.539
Forget the past.

00:51:59.539 --> 00:52:04.680
But this is also another problem of the West
is: now their forefathers say came here and

00:52:04.680 --> 00:52:05.970
killed some Red Indians.

00:52:05.970 --> 00:52:10.470
Now, the forefathers are finished, they might
have become Red Indians in this lifetime.

00:52:10.470 --> 00:52:11.509
They are not there.

00:52:11.509 --> 00:52:13.799
You are their children's children's children's
children.

00:52:13.799 --> 00:52:17.199
Now why are you carrying on the jokes so far?

00:52:17.199 --> 00:52:22.529
But for everything they feel guilty - is another
such a mental nonsense that please, before

00:52:22.529 --> 00:52:27.910
I start this program, I have to request you
that don't feel guilty for anything.

00:52:27.910 --> 00:52:29.770
You have done nothing wrong.

00:52:29.770 --> 00:52:33.510
[Shri Mataji speaks aside] Also, there is
another two-three people.

00:52:33.510 --> 00:52:39.549
Question: Is Gorbachev is a walk-in, which
means that is he from some other place which

00:52:39.549 --> 00:52:40.549
is advanced soul?

00:52:40.549 --> 00:52:44.039
Shri Mataji: He is a realized soul, no doubt,
he is.

00:52:44.039 --> 00:52:45.640
That's why it's working out.

00:52:45.640 --> 00:52:47.240
He knows Me very well.

00:52:47.240 --> 00:52:48.849
He is a realized soul.

00:52:48.849 --> 00:52:52.160
That you recognized him, I'm very happy to
know that.

00:52:52.160 --> 00:52:55.259
He is and look at them, how lucky they are
to have him there.

00:52:55.259 --> 00:52:58.579
And, he is a very sensible man, no doubt.

00:52:58.579 --> 00:52:59.579
Even Lenin was.

00:52:59.579 --> 00:53:04.380
Lenin was a realized soul, you will be surprised,
but he was forced by all his party members.

00:53:04.380 --> 00:53:06.319
He was alone, you see.

00:53:06.319 --> 00:53:19.079
And, all of them forced him to take a course
of line which was really proved later on.

00:53:19.079 --> 00:53:37.420
But whatever was his state, talked about stateless
state and all that was his dream and that's

00:53:37.420 --> 00:53:39.569
coming true.

00:53:39.569 --> 00:53:44.109
He was also a realized soul.

00:53:44.109 --> 00:53:50.599
But he went onto a wrong line and it took
so much time for them to come back and they

00:53:50.599 --> 00:53:54.689
had horrible despotic people, no doubt but
the way the Gorbachev is doing is great and

00:53:54.689 --> 00:54:01.439
I have a rapport with him and he is a very
great man, I must say.

00:54:01.439 --> 00:54:04.880
And he has tremendous respect for Me.

00:54:04.880 --> 00:54:10.050
Because we are of the same style, you can
say, the same line, that's why.

00:54:10.050 --> 00:54:11.939
You, too, had in America.

00:54:11.939 --> 00:54:16.079
You had, say, Abraham Lincoln was a realized
soul, no doubt.

00:54:16.079 --> 00:54:17.969
And, we had Mahatma Gandhi.

00:54:17.969 --> 00:54:20.579
We had many people, but they were singled
out.

00:54:20.579 --> 00:54:22.400
They couldn't give realizations to others.

00:54:22.400 --> 00:54:27.199
They were singled out and they had to fight,
but now you all can become realized souls.

00:54:27.199 --> 00:54:32.150
We have to have many more to get peace, to
get joy, to get what we deserve.

00:54:32.150 --> 00:54:36.170
[Question: A lady seems to have some illness
that doctors can't diagnose and is asking

00:54:36.170 --> 00:54:37.819
if Shri Mataji can help.]

00:54:37.819 --> 00:54:39.470
Shri Mataji: Yes, that's true.

00:54:39.470 --> 00:54:41.119
I am Myself a doctor.

00:54:41.119 --> 00:54:42.450
I've done medicine, Myself.

00:54:42.450 --> 00:54:43.450
I know that.

00:54:43.450 --> 00:54:46.740
It's difficult for them because they cannot
raise the Kundalini.

00:54:46.740 --> 00:54:48.420
You see that's the problem is.

00:54:48.420 --> 00:54:50.480
Please sit down, I'll tell you.

00:54:50.480 --> 00:54:55.439
The medical science is, of course has reached
a quite a lot of height and have understood

00:54:55.439 --> 00:55:02.420
anything, but the problem with the medical
line is this: that when a tree is sick, you

00:55:02.420 --> 00:55:07.059
see, we treat the leaves but we cannot get
to the roots, you see.

00:55:07.059 --> 00:55:18.219
But Sahaja Yoga is a thing that gets to the
roots, and I'm not telling you off-hand, you

00:55:18.219 --> 00:55:22.579
see, there are three doctors who got their
Ph.D. in India in Sahaja Yoga that they have

00:55:22.579 --> 00:55:23.579
cured people.

00:55:23.579 --> 00:55:28.599
There are seven doctors in London who are
now writing down about how many people have

00:55:28.599 --> 00:55:30.630
been cured with Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:30.630 --> 00:55:36.059
But the problem is like this: like for in
America, I cannot cure people because I will

00:55:36.059 --> 00:55:37.059
be arrested.

00:55:37.059 --> 00:55:39.960
If and if Christ goes there, He will be arrested.

00:55:39.960 --> 00:55:44.019
The medical science doesn't allow there, I
mean, that anybody should cure anyone.

00:55:44.019 --> 00:55:49.890
Now, the problem is if you come to India nobody
is allowed to come to India who suffers with

00:55:49.890 --> 00:55:52.049
AIDS and all such diseases.

00:55:52.049 --> 00:55:54.650
Big problem for the patient also.

