00:56:55.609 --> 00:56:57.369
going to get to Sahaja Yoga, means that their
Kundalini doesn't rise.

00:56:57.369 --> 00:56:59.789
If their Kundalini doesn't rise, then how
can we cure?

00:56:59.789 --> 00:57:01.559
That's the only way we can cure people.

00:57:01.559 --> 00:57:07.079
So there are limitations also that your Kundalini
has to rise and then you can get cured.

00:57:07.079 --> 00:57:09.319
But there are many miracles which have happened.

00:57:09.319 --> 00:57:11.279
I don't know how people got cured.

00:57:11.279 --> 00:57:13.519
And there have been many cures, no doubt.

00:57:13.519 --> 00:57:16.699
And, it sounds very, very much fantastic that
it can be cured through Kundalini awakening

00:57:16.699 --> 00:57:17.699
but it has happened.

00:57:17.699 --> 00:57:18.699
We have to accept the truth.

00:57:18.699 --> 00:57:22.469
As long as it helps, what does it matter?

00:57:22.469 --> 00:57:23.469
Yes, please?

00:57:23.469 --> 00:57:27.069
Question: What would be the effect of increasing
number of Sahaja Yogis on the economic system

00:57:27.069 --> 00:57:33.219
and the lifestyle of the country where the
increase of Sahaja Yogis takes place?

00:57:33.219 --> 00:57:35.839
Shri Mataji: Oh, it just triggers everything.

00:57:35.839 --> 00:57:38.769
For example, now what are our problems?

00:57:38.769 --> 00:57:44.650
We see the economic problems of this country
is.

00:57:44.650 --> 00:57:53.699
I have understood it so well that we have
so much of a, say, ores and all other things

00:57:53.699 --> 00:58:00.619
like silver we have here, and gold and all
kinds of things we have, and the ones who

00:58:00.619 --> 00:58:04.529
are exploiting us are Americans and nobody
sees the point.

00:58:04.529 --> 00:58:05.599
Nobody sees the point.

00:58:05.599 --> 00:58:08.339
While those who will get Sahaja Yogis, they
will become so dynamic.

00:58:08.339 --> 00:58:12.819
They will put in their own industries here.

00:58:12.819 --> 00:58:14.499
Why send it?

00:58:14.499 --> 00:58:17.289
Why make cars in America?

00:58:17.289 --> 00:58:20.089
Why not make them here?

00:58:20.089 --> 00:58:27.940
So many things can happen because you become
so dynamic and there's so many people to help

00:58:27.940 --> 00:58:29.990
you all over that this is what should happen.

00:58:29.990 --> 00:58:33.539
After all, you have all kinds of things available
here.

00:58:33.539 --> 00:58:39.569
Why should you send your aluminum to America,
to be drawn into wires and beaten into sheets?

00:58:39.569 --> 00:58:40.630
There's no need.

00:58:40.630 --> 00:58:42.410
We can do it ourselves.

00:58:42.410 --> 00:58:46.960
So this, you see, self-confidence that we
can do it together and the collective feeling

00:58:46.960 --> 00:58:48.819
can give you such good ideas.

00:58:48.819 --> 00:58:53.769
And another point is that the way we are working
out machines now.

00:58:53.769 --> 00:58:56.650
Now we have to understand that machines are
for us.

00:58:56.650 --> 00:59:03.699
We have created machines and machines are
to be used according to our need and we are

00:59:03.699 --> 00:59:05.239
not for machines.

00:59:05.239 --> 00:59:08.329
They are not to dominate us.

00:59:08.329 --> 00:59:15.519
So as much as we need we'll use machines otherwise
we'll not use machines.

00:59:15.519 --> 00:59:22.759
And as a result, already it is happening that
people don't like machine-made things and

00:59:22.759 --> 00:59:23.759
machine-made this thing.

00:59:23.759 --> 00:59:27.859
So they will go to the balancing state where
they will take to more handmade things and

00:59:27.859 --> 00:59:28.859
handmade material.

00:59:28.859 --> 00:59:33.740
Now for a handmade things you don't have to
have so many.

00:59:33.740 --> 00:59:39.799
Like, now we say in India, thank God, we are
quite poor country, we can't afford to have

00:59:39.799 --> 00:59:40.809
so many machines.

00:59:40.809 --> 00:59:46.869
Thank God for that because now in a household
they will have about, say, ten plates of brass

00:59:46.869 --> 00:59:48.549
or twelve plates of brass.

00:59:48.549 --> 00:59:49.549
Finished.

00:59:49.549 --> 00:59:53.259
We don't have to have so many crockery, cutlery,
this, that, that breaks.

00:59:53.259 --> 00:59:55.660
Then, after that you have plastic.

00:59:55.660 --> 01:00:02.680
Because it breaks so you have plastics.

01:00:02.680 --> 01:00:06.689
So, you go on.

01:00:06.689 --> 01:00:12.969
The plastic is now mounting up, mountains
after mountains we have created.

01:00:12.969 --> 01:00:16.289
So, you take more to practical side, very
much practical and more to the natural.

01:00:16.289 --> 01:00:20.089
And in natural, it's nice to have one natural
thing than to have ten plastics.

01:00:20.089 --> 01:00:24.209
Now people are realizing, I'm not saying they
are not realizing it.

01:00:24.209 --> 01:00:27.309
But still there are machines sitting on top
of us.

01:00:27.309 --> 01:00:30.420
And then the entrepreneurs, the entrepreneurs
are very clever.

01:00:30.420 --> 01:00:34.569
Today they start one fashions, tomorrow another
fashion, third day third fashion.

01:00:34.569 --> 01:00:37.160
England is another one who suffers a lot.

01:00:37.160 --> 01:00:41.789
For example, in a place like London, which
is such a cold place, people have pants which

01:00:41.789 --> 01:00:43.309
have holes in it.

01:00:43.309 --> 01:00:45.179
They call it holy pants, you see.

01:00:45.179 --> 01:00:49.039
And now imagine, they developed varicose veins
with that.

01:00:49.039 --> 01:00:51.189
Or they'll have tight pants.

01:00:51.189 --> 01:00:52.579
They have to do something about it.

01:00:52.579 --> 01:00:54.289
They have to feed their machines.

01:00:54.289 --> 01:00:57.349
So they will start this fashion or that fashion.

01:00:57.349 --> 01:01:02.450
Now, there's another fashion which is also
very dangerous that people don't put any oil

01:01:02.450 --> 01:01:03.470
in their hair.

01:01:03.470 --> 01:01:09.119
Before taking a head bath, one can put easily
some oil or before night they can put it.

01:01:09.119 --> 01:01:10.640
They are all getting bald.

01:01:10.640 --> 01:01:13.390
Once they get bald, them they'll sell their
wigs.

01:01:13.390 --> 01:01:16.859
The same hair which are fallen off, they make
wigs and sell it.

01:01:16.859 --> 01:01:17.859
They are befooling you.

01:01:17.859 --> 01:01:22.990
If you see little bit, you stand out and see
how they are befooling you must, these entrepreneurs

01:01:22.990 --> 01:01:23.990
are.

01:01:23.990 --> 01:01:27.490
This is the fashion today, that is the fashion.

01:01:27.490 --> 01:01:32.839
I was seeing the children, we are now producing
clothes for children, for example.

01:01:32.839 --> 01:01:35.009
The clothes are such horrible clothes.

01:01:35.009 --> 01:01:36.559
I mean, they call them...

01:01:36.559 --> 01:01:41.369
[Shri Mataji asks someone in Hindi, "What
do they call such clothes now-a-days?"]

01:01:41.369 --> 01:01:42.499
... trendy, trendy clothes.

01:01:42.499 --> 01:01:44.019
Children wear trendy clothes.

01:01:44.019 --> 01:01:46.660
They have no respect, respect for themselves.

01:01:46.660 --> 01:01:48.179
They don't respect themselves.

01:01:48.179 --> 01:01:55.519
If you give them trendy clothes, you see,
they become like brats, and then you say they

01:01:55.519 --> 01:01:56.849
are brats.

01:01:56.849 --> 01:02:01.539
You make them brats from very childhood.

01:02:01.539 --> 01:02:06.490
You want them to be brats, you see.

01:02:06.490 --> 01:02:09.940
So,the whole system changes.

01:02:09.940 --> 01:02:15.119
Children become so beautiful, so dignified.

01:02:15.119 --> 01:02:25.480
Dress makes a person understand what is his
personality is, isn't it?

01:02:25.480 --> 01:02:34.709
If you are just sort of careless about everything,
you are not bothered and the way - I have

01:02:34.709 --> 01:02:41.890
seen also children and even the grown-ups
walk as if you see the, it doesn't matter

01:02:41.890 --> 01:02:49.950
how you walk, you throw your legs this side,
hands like that.

01:02:49.950 --> 01:02:58.289
That shows the personality, that this personality
has no sense of dignity - how it has to walk,

01:02:58.289 --> 01:03:01.329
how they have to talk or things.

01:03:01.329 --> 01:03:05.240
So the whole thing has come down.

01:03:05.240 --> 01:03:08.960
Now, for example, English language now.

01:03:08.960 --> 01:03:18.150
I never studied English language but when
I went to England, I was surprised the kind

01:03:18.150 --> 01:03:20.469
of English they are speaking.

01:03:20.469 --> 01:03:25.660
I mean, you don't know what sort of English
they are speaking.

01:03:25.660 --> 01:03:27.329
And, really is impossible.

01:03:27.329 --> 01:03:39.940
At least, in Canada people speak better English,
I tell you.

01:03:39.940 --> 01:03:49.239
You'll have a language problem, really.

01:03:49.239 --> 01:04:01.029
Because they, even people from Cambridge,
they have developed such funny, funny intonations

01:04:01.029 --> 01:04:05.999
and funny pronunciation that it's impossible
to cope with them.

01:04:05.999 --> 01:04:12.109
So this is what I'm trying to tell you: that
once you get this balance, once you get this

01:04:12.109 --> 01:04:16.680
knowledge, you develop a balanced economy,
you develop a balanced ecology, you develop

01:04:16.680 --> 01:04:19.859
everything in balance because all these imbalances
has come through human beings.

01:04:19.859 --> 01:04:21.969
What is the source is a human being.

01:04:21.969 --> 01:04:25.130
You see, in the jungle if you go there's no
imbalance.

01:04:25.130 --> 01:04:27.490
Only where human beings live there's imbalance.

01:04:27.490 --> 01:04:33.719
So once you get into balance, when you have
more Sahaja Yogis, there will be more balance

01:04:33.719 --> 01:04:37.499
and you'll be surprised how things will work
out.

01:04:37.499 --> 01:04:42.819
And, above all there is this Divine Power
which is going to help you.

01:04:42.819 --> 01:04:45.400
Now, what do you want again?

01:04:45.400 --> 01:04:47.549
Question: Can we meditate now?

01:04:47.549 --> 01:04:53.680
Now, I hope you are finished with your questions,
because if you finish with questions it's

01:04:53.680 --> 01:04:56.700
better because this mind, you know, is a funny
thing.

01:04:56.700 --> 01:05:01.229
Suddenly, you're meditating, suddenly a thing
will come, "Oh, I should have asked this question

01:05:01.229 --> 01:05:02.229
to Mother!"

01:05:02.229 --> 01:05:07.900
But as she says it's true that even if I answer
all your questions, it's a mental acrobat.

01:05:07.900 --> 01:05:10.549
I can answer all your questions very well.

01:05:10.549 --> 01:05:18.220
I am good at it, but it is not going to raise
your Kundalini.

01:05:18.220 --> 01:05:24.369
So no question, is better that you just see
that what happens because it's a happening

01:05:24.369 --> 01:05:25.640
within yourself.

01:05:25.640 --> 01:05:27.349
It takes you without thinking about it.

01:05:27.349 --> 01:05:31.569
It takes you beyond the state where you become
thoughtlessly aware.

01:05:31.569 --> 01:05:34.660
You are aware but the thoughts absolutely
subside.

01:05:34.660 --> 01:05:44.249
And then ultimately you feel a cool breeze
coming out of your head and you feel cool

01:05:44.249 --> 01:05:47.539
breeze all around you.

01:05:47.539 --> 01:05:52.420
This is what has to happen.

01:05:52.420 --> 01:06:00.209
And I'm very happy that she has pointed out
that they are all waiting for it.

01:06:00.209 --> 01:06:03.349
And, there's no end to these talks and things.

01:06:03.349 --> 01:06:08.969
So, if you have any questions you may write
to Me or you may give Me in writing, if you

01:06:08.969 --> 01:06:11.209
feel that it is such an important question.

01:06:11.209 --> 01:06:18.689
Then, of course, these people will definitely
try to give you an answer for that.

01:06:18.689 --> 01:06:25.449
Now, I have I think in thousands My lectures
are there and the tapes are available.

01:06:25.449 --> 01:06:32.809
But we do not give people the lectures and
the books and things because once it starts

01:06:32.809 --> 01:06:35.729
the mental activity they just run into that.

01:06:35.729 --> 01:06:42.880
So, first of all develop yourself internally
into that abstract stage and then if you read,

01:06:42.880 --> 01:06:44.369
it has some meaning.

01:06:44.369 --> 01:06:51.279
Otherwise, there are people who know everything
about Sahaja Yoga but they can't do anything

01:06:51.279 --> 01:06:52.279
about it.

01:06:52.279 --> 01:06:54.499
Still there are two persons.

01:06:54.499 --> 01:06:58.049
Now these are the last two persons, all right?

01:06:58.049 --> 01:06:59.589
Now, what's it madam?

01:06:59.589 --> 01:07:04.349
Question: When do you feel the throbbing feeling
when the Kundalini rises, when pulsation is

01:07:04.349 --> 01:07:05.349
there?

01:07:05.349 --> 01:07:12.319
You see, actually, Kundalini is in this jet
age has become like a jet Kundalini.

01:07:12.319 --> 01:07:18.669
She just rises, She doesn't give you much
throbbing or anything - normally, normally

01:07:18.669 --> 01:07:19.669
I'm saying.

01:07:19.669 --> 01:07:25.049
But if you have some troubles, some diseases,
something, some obstructions, then it does

01:07:25.049 --> 01:07:26.259
throb a little.

01:07:26.259 --> 01:07:33.109
But you can feel it nicely on your head the
cool breeze coming out of your fontanel bone

01:07:33.109 --> 01:07:36.079
area, very nicely, you see it, you feel it.

01:07:36.079 --> 01:07:47.119
So it is the throbbing of the Kundalini and
all that are just like some sort of an obstructions

01:07:47.119 --> 01:07:52.440
or say, short circuiting but that can be corrected
very easily.

01:07:52.440 --> 01:07:57.930
So, it's like a very nicely built, very efficiently
built aeroplane, has a very smooth landing,

01:07:57.930 --> 01:07:59.990
like that Kundalini rises very beautifully.

01:07:59.990 --> 01:08:04.079
And, this is the blessing of the modern times,
I think, that the Kundalini works out that

01:08:04.079 --> 01:08:05.509
way.

01:08:05.509 --> 01:08:07.700
There's one more, there was one gentleman.

01:08:07.700 --> 01:08:13.039
Question: The question is that once the Kundalini
is awaken he's read that Kundalini can be

01:08:13.039 --> 01:08:18.580
if uncontrolled, if you don't know how to
control it, can it harm you?

01:08:18.580 --> 01:08:21.620
You see, these books are written by people
who have no idea of Kundalini.

01:08:21.620 --> 01:08:23.159
It's not like that.

01:08:23.159 --> 01:08:25.889
You see, this is just to sell something.

01:08:25.889 --> 01:08:26.889
It's marketing.

01:08:26.889 --> 01:08:28.900
Sell anything, any nonsense, there's nothing.

01:08:28.900 --> 01:08:30.400
She is your Mother.

01:08:30.400 --> 01:08:35.289
She is your individual Mother who's waiting
to give you your second birth.

01:08:35.289 --> 01:08:37.170
Why will She trouble you?

01:08:37.170 --> 01:08:42.809
When you got your birth, your mother looked
after everything, she, poor thing, went through

01:08:42.809 --> 01:08:48.049
all the labor pains and everything, she didn't
allow you to suffer anything, she never wanted

01:08:48.049 --> 01:08:49.049
you to suffer.

01:08:49.049 --> 01:08:50.049
Did she?

01:08:50.049 --> 01:08:56.450
Then this is a pure Mother, your own individual
Mother; She knows each and everything about

01:08:56.450 --> 01:08:57.450
you.

01:08:57.450 --> 01:09:04.000
It's all recorded in Her and She is not going
to trouble you, and you are going to be controlled

01:09:04.000 --> 01:09:08.759
by Her in such a manner that She becomes your
energy.

01:09:08.759 --> 01:09:10.469
She helps you.

01:09:10.469 --> 01:09:19.039
So, all these false ideas people have given,
written books after books so that they can

01:09:19.039 --> 01:09:20.039
sell it.

01:09:20.039 --> 01:09:21.299
I haven't written any books so far.

01:09:21.299 --> 01:09:23.809
You'll be surprised, I've not written any
books so far.

01:09:23.809 --> 01:09:26.079
Twenty years have past, I've written no books
whatsoever.

01:09:26.079 --> 01:09:29.599
People have written about Me, people have
written about Sahaja Yoga, they have written

01:09:29.599 --> 01:09:34.929
all this, but I have not yet written.

01:09:34.929 --> 01:09:39.560
I'll be writing.

01:09:39.560 --> 01:09:50.869
I hope so I get some time to write.

01:09:50.869 --> 01:09:54.170
But you see, what is important is that whatever
written can be all nonsense.

01:09:54.170 --> 01:09:58.490
They can write anything about anything.

01:09:58.490 --> 01:10:04.139
First of all, you should know what it is.

01:10:04.139 --> 01:10:08.139
And now I have been going to various places,
I have not seen it misbehaving anywhere or

01:10:08.139 --> 01:10:09.440
doing any harm to anybody.

01:10:09.440 --> 01:10:17.699
Of course, sometimes you do feel little heat
in the body, that's all.

01:10:17.699 --> 01:10:29.800
That's the thing you feel little heat on your
hands, that's all.

01:10:29.800 --> 01:10:33.800
But it's so little that it's negligible.

01:10:33.800 --> 01:10:35.200
So, be confident.

01:10:35.200 --> 01:10:47.650
First of all, before starting I have to tell
you few things and one of them is that have

01:10:47.650 --> 01:10:48.650
faith in yourself.

01:10:48.650 --> 01:10:54.469
Have faith that you all are capable of getting
your Self-realization.

01:10:54.469 --> 01:10:57.329
Please have that faith in yourself.

01:10:57.329 --> 01:11:04.640
You have faith in everything else but in yourself,
that's wrong.

01:11:04.640 --> 01:11:07.280
Please have faith in yourself.

01:11:07.280 --> 01:11:09.630
That is first point.

01:11:09.630 --> 01:11:14.510
Now there are two conditions we have to fulfill
before we get our realization.

01:11:14.510 --> 01:11:21.870
First condition is I have already told you,
that not to feel guilty, forget the past.

01:11:21.870 --> 01:11:28.550
Not to feel guilty is very important because
when you feel guilty, then the center here

01:11:28.550 --> 01:11:35.010
on the left side catches, Vishuddhi as they
call it, and it's the worst thing that can

01:11:35.010 --> 01:11:40.719
happen because this is the center when it
catches you get spondylitis, you get angina,

01:11:40.719 --> 01:11:43.580
all kinds of trouble with this center.

01:11:43.580 --> 01:11:48.920
But the worst thing is that the Kundalini
cannot rise above this center.

01:11:48.920 --> 01:11:52.880
So, not to feel guilty.

01:11:52.880 --> 01:12:00.060
I assure you that you have done nothing wrong.

01:12:00.060 --> 01:12:02.260
You see, there are so many norms a society
has created.

01:12:02.260 --> 01:12:08.750
Even if you put the fork on the other side
you start thinking, "Oh God, what did I do?"

01:12:08.750 --> 01:12:15.869
You feel you are not sophisticated or you
have done something like a murder.

01:12:15.869 --> 01:12:17.389
It's not that.

01:12:17.389 --> 01:12:24.369
It is just all these norms are artificially
created, all these are artificial things.

01:12:24.369 --> 01:12:30.239
Somebody is very thin, he thinks, "Why should
I be thin?"

01:12:30.239 --> 01:12:35.039
Somebody's fat, he says, "Why should I be
fat?"

01:12:35.039 --> 01:12:42.909
But this is life's, whatever is there we have
to accept our life as it is and there's nothing

01:12:42.909 --> 01:12:44.110
wrong in it.

01:12:44.110 --> 01:12:45.110
Nothing guilt.

01:12:45.110 --> 01:12:50.900
Whatever is there, whatever we have been doing,
we have been doing as human beings.

01:12:50.900 --> 01:12:57.719
So, first and foremost condition is - absolutely
you cannot compromise on that - is that you

01:12:57.719 --> 01:13:00.180
are not to feel guilty at all.

01:13:00.180 --> 01:13:01.820
Immediately, you'll feel better.

01:13:01.820 --> 01:13:06.920
All right, the second one is that you have
to forgive everyone, forgive everyone because

01:13:06.920 --> 01:13:09.699
whether you forgive or you don't forgive,
you don't do anything.

01:13:09.699 --> 01:13:18.550
You are living with a myth, all the time thinking,
"Oh, I have to forgive this person, I have

01:13:18.550 --> 01:13:20.489
to forgive that person."

01:13:20.489 --> 01:13:23.889
There's no need to think like that.

01:13:23.889 --> 01:13:34.829
You don't also have to think about any individual,
just in general you have to say, "I forgive

01:13:34.829 --> 01:13:36.429
everyone of them."

01:13:36.429 --> 01:13:45.330
And, that clears out this center, very clearly,
this is the center of Christ, this clears

01:13:45.330 --> 01:13:51.000
out, and it's very easy for Me because this
is a very constricted, it's the gate to the

01:13:51.000 --> 01:14:01.780
limbic area so that gate has to be widened
and it has to be opened out.

01:14:01.780 --> 01:14:03.930
And so, just forgive everyone.

01:14:03.930 --> 01:14:07.310
And, you know it is a myth.

01:14:07.310 --> 01:14:09.780
You are playing into the wrong hands.

01:14:09.780 --> 01:14:13.100
So, this is another condition, you have to
just accept.

01:14:13.100 --> 01:14:18.409
Then it's easier for Me to work it out and
easier for you to get it.

01:14:18.409 --> 01:14:19.860
So, first is just don't feel guilty.

01:14:19.860 --> 01:14:22.480
If you don't forgive, you won't feel it.

01:14:22.480 --> 01:14:26.070
Then, you will come and say, "Mother, I didn't
feel it."

01:14:26.070 --> 01:14:29.659
And then I'll have to say, "All right, forgive,
forgive, forgive."

01:14:29.659 --> 01:14:31.300
And then you'll feel it.

01:14:31.300 --> 01:14:32.719
So, what's the use?

01:14:32.719 --> 01:14:41.409
Just better do what I've told you, is very
simple thing, just forgive everyone in general.

01:14:41.409 --> 01:14:49.980
Then there are certain simple things: that
we have to take help of the Mother Earth.

01:14:49.980 --> 01:14:57.199
Now those who are sitting in the ground are
the best placed, that's all right, they can

01:14:57.199 --> 01:15:10.390
just take out their shoes, so they're not,
it's better that their feet are a little open

01:15:10.390 --> 01:15:11.390
out.

01:15:11.390 --> 01:15:16.900
And, all of you should have to take your feet
out, it helps a lot.

01:15:16.900 --> 01:15:22.579
Those who are sitting, should sit more cross-legged
it's better, better to sit cross legged.

01:15:22.579 --> 01:15:28.250
It's hardly will take any time and is ... you
don't have to fight with your thoughts, you

01:15:28.250 --> 01:15:31.059
don't have to stop your thoughts, nothing,
it just works automatically.

01:15:31.059 --> 01:15:35.440
I would say, like your attention is like this
saree.

01:15:35.440 --> 01:15:43.530
Now, the Kundalini rises like this, goes up
and She pushes all your attention inside automatically

01:15:43.530 --> 01:15:48.139
and then when it pierces through here, then
the grace starts falling on your attention,

01:15:48.139 --> 01:15:50.030
on your sympathetic nervous system and it
soothes down.

01:15:50.030 --> 01:15:52.889
Then, your centers open more and more threads
of Kundalini rise.

01:15:52.889 --> 01:16:00.760
So, this is what is today's modern Sahaja
Yoga, which somehow or other I've managed

01:16:00.760 --> 01:16:07.239
to discover, that let few threads of Kundalini
rise to begin with so that you open your chakras

01:16:07.239 --> 01:16:09.190
gradually, and then more and more.

01:16:09.190 --> 01:16:11.940
And then one day I find you all have become
great gurus, great personalities.

01:16:11.940 --> 01:16:13.110
So, may God bless you all!

01:16:13.110 --> 01:16:18.520
So, let us now with all respect to ourselves,
with all love for ourselves, we have to have

01:16:18.520 --> 01:16:20.159
complete faith in ourselves, complete faith.

01:16:20.159 --> 01:16:21.159
Have complete self confidence.

01:16:21.159 --> 01:16:23.099
Now please put both your hands like this.

01:16:23.099 --> 01:16:26.530
It's important to understand that these five,
six and seven are the sympathetic nervous

01:16:26.530 --> 01:16:27.530
system endings and this side also are, these
are sympathetic nervous system endings and

01:16:27.530 --> 01:16:30.420
they are the ones who are expressing the centers
within ourselves.

01:16:30.420 --> 01:16:34.200
Like this, left and right meet and make one
center.

01:16:34.200 --> 01:16:41.080
So, is very important that you, we have to
put both the hands like this to begin with.

01:16:41.080 --> 01:16:49.070
You can, now somebody will show you how we
are going to nourish our centers.

01:16:49.070 --> 01:16:54.920
The left side represents our desire, not the
pure desire, but our desire.

01:16:54.920 --> 01:17:07.870
And the right side represents our action,
power of action.

01:17:07.870 --> 01:17:14.989
So, we will be using our power of action to
nourish our centers, while the left hand will

01:17:14.989 --> 01:17:16.940
be all the time towards Myself.

01:17:16.940 --> 01:17:23.200
Before closing your eyes, you can also take
out your spectacles because this helps eyesight

01:17:23.200 --> 01:17:24.200
also.

01:17:24.200 --> 01:17:33.719
So before, not now, just now when I tell to,
because just now I'll show you how to do it

01:17:33.719 --> 01:17:37.320
and then we'll close our eyes.

01:17:37.320 --> 01:17:39.280
So somebody will show you.

01:17:39.280 --> 01:17:43.580
First of all, you put your left hand toward
Me like this.

01:17:43.580 --> 01:17:50.670
Of course, those who don't want to do it,
should go because it is proper not to disturb

01:17:50.670 --> 01:17:51.670
others.

01:17:51.670 --> 01:17:59.719
You see, nobody should, those who do not want
to do should try to do it because it's not

01:17:59.719 --> 01:18:07.349
proper and should not disturb others in between
to get up and walk out.

01:18:07.349 --> 01:18:12.640
So, now please put your left hand towards
Me like this.

01:18:12.640 --> 01:18:16.820
And, with the right hand we nourish our centers.

01:18:16.820 --> 01:18:20.550
So, first we put it on our heart.

01:18:20.550 --> 01:18:25.670
In the heart, resides the Spirit, is reflected
in the Spirit.

01:18:25.670 --> 01:18:41.469
Spirit is the reflection of God Almighty and
Kundalini is the reflection of the primordial

01:18:41.469 --> 01:19:06.750
power, His desire which we call as Adi Shakti
or we call it as Holy Ghost.

01:19:06.750 --> 01:19:14.780
These two have to meet, and the seat of the
Spirit is on the fontanel bone area here,

01:19:14.780 --> 01:19:18.949
seat of the Spirit is here, but it resides
in our heart.

01:19:18.949 --> 01:19:28.250
Now, so first we put our right hand on our
heart and then we put our right hand in the

01:19:28.250 --> 01:19:34.099
upper portion of our abdomen where is the
center of our mastery.

01:19:34.099 --> 01:19:40.429
This is created by all the great masters like
Abraham, Moses, Lao Tse, so many of them who

01:19:40.429 --> 01:19:42.610
were real masters.

01:19:42.610 --> 01:19:45.530
They have created this.

01:19:45.530 --> 01:19:52.659
Like Guru Nanaka, Janaka, all these people
have created this great center within us.

01:19:52.659 --> 01:19:59.530
Then we take down our hand in the lower portion
of our abdomen on the left hand side.

01:19:59.530 --> 01:20:08.199
This is the center of pure knowledge, pure
knowledge that is the one which gives us the

01:20:08.199 --> 01:20:10.640
awareness on our central nervous system.

01:20:10.640 --> 01:20:17.150
It manifests a new dimension in our awareness
on our central nervous system which is called

01:20:17.150 --> 01:20:26.060
in Sanskrit as bodh, bodh from where the word
Buddha has come, or we can say it manifests

01:20:26.060 --> 01:20:27.390
in the word, vidh.

01:20:27.390 --> 01:20:29.100
Vidh is from where Vedas have come.

01:20:29.100 --> 01:20:33.420
That you feel the divine power on your central
nervous system, you feel the truth on your

01:20:33.420 --> 01:20:38.519
central nervous system because whatever we
have gained in our evolution, you feel it

01:20:38.519 --> 01:20:40.320
on our central nervous system.

01:20:40.320 --> 01:20:42.630
That is what is "to know."

01:20:42.630 --> 01:20:44.170
Knowledge is not mental.

01:20:44.170 --> 01:20:50.329
It is in our evolutionary process to know
on your central nervous system like hot and

01:20:50.329 --> 01:20:51.329
cold.

01:20:51.329 --> 01:20:54.820
So now, this is the center which manifests
that pure knowledge.

01:20:54.820 --> 01:21:05.150
So, now we take our hand again upward and
put it on the center of mastery which is on

01:21:05.150 --> 01:21:15.560
the left hand side in the upper part of our
abdomen.

01:21:15.560 --> 01:21:43.490
Then we take our hand onto our heart, and
here we know that Spirit resides here.

01:21:43.490 --> 01:21:51.699
Then we take our hand in the corner of our
neck and our shoulder here and put it back

01:21:51.699 --> 01:21:58.050
as far as possible and turn our head to our
right, we turn our head to our right.

01:21:58.050 --> 01:22:38.289
This is the center which as I have told you
is always in trouble when we feel guilty and

01:22:38.289 --> 01:22:44.929
today also I feel it's quite a lot among the
people who are here.

01:22:44.929 --> 01:22:50.139
So, now please remember not to feel guilty
at all.

01:22:50.139 --> 01:23:02.159
Turn your head to your right and just not
to feel guilty, is very important.

01:23:02.159 --> 01:23:15.590
Now then we put our hand across like this
on our forehead and pressing on both the temples

01:23:15.590 --> 01:23:37.900
with our small finger and our thumb on another
side we put all the other fingers on the head

01:23:37.900 --> 01:23:43.599
and put down our head like this.

01:23:43.599 --> 01:23:52.570
This is the center, this is the center for
forgiving others.

01:23:52.570 --> 01:23:54.199
Forgive everyone.

01:23:54.199 --> 01:24:03.630
Now, we take back this hand on the back side
of our head on the optic lobe here, on the

01:24:03.630 --> 01:24:17.940
back side of our head and push back our head
as far back as possible resting on our hand,

01:24:17.940 --> 01:24:54.769
and here is the center without feeling guilty,
without counting any mistakes, just for your

01:24:54.769 --> 01:25:01.809
satisfaction to ask for forgiveness from the
divine power.

01:25:01.809 --> 01:25:15.260
Now, then we stretch our hand, stretch our
hand and the center of our palm, we put it

01:25:15.260 --> 01:25:25.139
on the fontanel bone area which was the soft
bone in our childhood.

01:25:25.139 --> 01:25:40.630
Now we put down your head, put down our head
and press this area nicely by pushing our

01:25:40.630 --> 01:25:42.349
fingers outward.

01:25:42.349 --> 01:25:56.159
This is very important thing to do is to push
back your fingers outward so there's nice

01:25:56.159 --> 01:26:01.130
pressure on your fontanel bone area.

01:26:01.130 --> 01:26:13.409
Now here is the limbic area, the opening of
the limbic area is the fontanel bone area.

01:26:13.409 --> 01:26:22.260
So now what we do is to now slowly move our
hand clockwise pressing the scalp, move the

01:26:22.260 --> 01:26:26.019
scalp, clockwise, seven times.

01:26:26.019 --> 01:26:34.260
Push down your head, it's better, then you
can do it better, move it seven times clockwise.

01:26:34.260 --> 01:26:42.349
Now, I think everything was done all right
but we didn't push back the fingers nicely

01:26:42.349 --> 01:26:49.949
and the pressure was less but doesn't matter.

01:26:49.949 --> 01:26:57.030
Now, so, you have been already told what is
to be done.

01:26:57.030 --> 01:27:11.010
Now please, again see that you put both your
feet away from each other because they are

01:27:11.010 --> 01:27:14.519
two different powers.

01:27:14.519 --> 01:27:25.321
Put your left hand towards Me, put your right
hand on your head.

01:27:25.321 --> 01:27:26.321
No, not like that, you can sit, I mean you
can sit cross legged, cross legged is better,

01:27:26.321 --> 01:27:27.321
it's all right, for sitting down this cross
legged is better.

01:27:27.321 --> 01:27:28.321
I am just telling for people who are sitting
on the chairs.

01:27:28.321 --> 01:27:29.321
Just imagine people getting realization sitting
on the chairs.

01:27:29.321 --> 01:27:30.321
Is something great, isn't it?

01:27:30.321 --> 01:27:31.321
Otherwise, we had to go to Himalayas and starve
for so many days, work so hard, stand on your

01:27:31.321 --> 01:27:32.321
heads and still come back empty handed.

01:27:32.321 --> 01:27:33.321
You are specially blessed to be born in this
era.

01:27:33.321 --> 01:27:34.321
All right, so now we put our left hand towards
Me, and right hand on the heart and now we

01:27:34.321 --> 01:27:35.321
close our eyes.

01:27:35.321 --> 01:27:36.321
We don't open our eyes till I tell you.

01:27:36.321 --> 01:27:37.321
Please keep your eyes shut till I tell you.

01:27:37.321 --> 01:27:38.321
Now, the whole thing works like a divine computer,
so you have to ask a question.

01:27:38.321 --> 01:27:39.321
You can call Me Mother or you can call Me
Shri Mataji, whatever you like.

01:27:39.321 --> 01:27:40.321
Now, put your right hand on your heart and
left hand towards Me all the time.

01:27:40.321 --> 01:27:41.321
And, now sit comfortably, not bending too
much nor in a stretched manner but in a comfortable,

01:27:41.321 --> 01:27:42.321
straight way.

01:27:42.321 --> 01:27:43.321
Here now you ask a question three times, "Mother,
am I the Spirit?"

01:27:43.321 --> 01:27:44.321
This is the truth about you that you are the
Spirit.

01:27:44.321 --> 01:27:45.321
So now ask the question three times in your
heart, "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:27:45.321 --> 01:27:46.321
Now, if you are the Spirit, then you are your
master.

01:27:46.321 --> 01:27:47.321
So, now take your right hand in the upper
portion of your abdomen and ask a question,

01:27:47.321 --> 01:27:48.321
"Mother, am I my own master?"

01:27:48.321 --> 01:27:49.321
Ask this question three times.

01:27:49.321 --> 01:27:50.321
Now I have to tell you that I cannot force
pure knowledge on you.

01:27:50.321 --> 01:27:51.321
You have to ask for it.

01:27:51.321 --> 01:27:52.321
So, now please take your hand in the lower
portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

01:27:52.321 --> 01:27:53.321
Here you have to say six times, because this
center has got six petals.

01:27:53.321 --> 01:27:54.321
So, please say, "Mother, please give me pure
knowledge."

01:27:54.321 --> 01:27:55.321
Say this six times because I cannot force
on you.

01:27:55.321 --> 01:27:56.321
You have to ask in your freedom.

01:27:56.321 --> 01:27:57.321
I respect it.

01:27:57.321 --> 01:27:58.321
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge, the
Kundalini starts rising, so we have to nourish

01:27:58.321 --> 01:27:59.321
the upper centers so that it's easy for Her
to rise.

01:27:59.321 --> 01:28:00.321
So, now take your right hand in the upper
portion of your abdomen on the left hand side,

01:28:00.321 --> 01:28:01.321
press it hard.

01:28:01.321 --> 01:28:02.321
Here, you have to say with full confidence
ten times, "Mother, I am my own master."

01:28:02.321 --> 01:28:03.321
Say it with full confidence in yourself, ten
times, "Mother, I am my own master."

01:28:03.321 --> 01:28:04.321
Now, raise your right hand on your heart.

01:28:04.321 --> 01:28:05.321
I have already told you that Spirit resides
in your heart, so now here you say with full

01:28:05.321 --> 01:28:06.321
confidence, twelve times, "Mother, I am the
Spirit."

01:28:06.321 --> 01:28:07.321
We have to know this all-pervading power which
has created us, which is nourishing us, which

01:28:07.321 --> 01:28:08.321
is looking after us, which organizes us and
which loves us, is the ocean of knowledge

01:28:08.321 --> 01:28:09.321
and compassion.

01:28:09.321 --> 01:28:10.321
But above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness,
and we cannot commit any mistakes that cannot

01:28:10.321 --> 01:28:11.321
be dissolved by the power of this ocean of
forgiveness.

01:28:11.321 --> 01:28:12.321
So, now please raise your hand in the corner
of your neck and your shoulder and push it

01:28:12.321 --> 01:28:13.321
back as far as possible on the spinal cord
and turn your head to right.

01:28:13.321 --> 01:28:14.321
And here, with full confidence, please say
sixteen times, "Mother, I am not guilty at

01:28:14.321 --> 01:28:15.321
all."

01:28:15.321 --> 01:28:16.321
Please say it sixteen times from your heart,
please say it.

01:28:16.321 --> 01:28:17.321
I have already told you that whether you forgive
or don't forgive, you do not do anything,

01:28:17.321 --> 01:28:18.321
it's a myth.

01:28:18.321 --> 01:28:19.321
But, if you don't forgive then you play into
wrong hands and torture yourself for nothing

01:28:19.321 --> 01:28:20.321
at all.

01:28:20.321 --> 01:28:21.321
So, now please raise your right hand on your
forehead across pressing both the temples

01:28:21.321 --> 01:28:22.321
with your small finger and your thumb and
putting all the three fingers on top of your

01:28:22.321 --> 01:28:23.321
head.

01:28:23.321 --> 01:28:24.321
And now, put it down your head properly, press
it hard on both the sides.

01:28:24.321 --> 01:28:25.321
And here you have to say from your heart,
not how many times, "Mother, I forgive everyone."

01:28:25.321 --> 01:28:26.321
From your heart, please say, "Mother, I forgive
everyone."

01:28:26.321 --> 01:28:27.321
Please do not say that it is difficult.

01:28:27.321 --> 01:28:28.321
It's the easiest thing to say.

01:28:28.321 --> 01:28:29.321
Put down your head properly, press it hard
and say it from your heart.

01:28:29.321 --> 01:28:33.199
Now, without feeling guilty, without counting
your mistakes, just for your satisfaction,

01:28:33.199 --> 01:28:39.699
you have to ask forgiveness from the Divine
Power.

01:28:39.699 --> 01:28:48.360
So, now take your right hand on the back side
of your head and push back your head as far

01:28:48.360 --> 01:28:53.330
as possible, on the hand balancing.

01:28:53.330 --> 01:29:05.730
Now here, you have to say again from your
heart, now how many times, "Oh Divine Power,

01:29:05.730 --> 01:29:13.179
if I have done anything wrong knowingly or
unknowingly, please forgive me."

01:29:13.179 --> 01:29:16.849
This is to be said for your own satisfaction.

01:29:16.849 --> 01:29:25.100
Push back your head as much as possible.

01:29:25.100 --> 01:29:40.409
Now, the last center which is most important:
stretch your palm as far as possible, put

01:29:40.409 --> 01:29:56.650
it on, put the center of your palm on top
of the fontanel bone area which was the soft

01:29:56.650 --> 01:29:59.210
bone in your childhood.

01:29:59.210 --> 01:30:06.559
Now put down your head as much as you can,
please put it down.

01:30:06.559 --> 01:30:09.219
Now, stretch your fingers.

01:30:09.219 --> 01:30:16.800
Please stretch them properly and put a nice
pressure on your fontanel bone area.

01:30:16.800 --> 01:30:24.869
Here, again I respect your freedom and I cannot
force Self-realization on you.

01:30:24.869 --> 01:30:27.300
You have to ask for it.

01:30:27.300 --> 01:30:40.280
So, now please move your scalp, slowly, seven
times, clockwise, saying, "Mother, please

01:30:40.280 --> 01:30:41.949
give me my Self-realization."

01:30:41.949 --> 01:31:37.430
[Mother blows in the microphone seven times.]

01:31:37.430 --> 01:31:53.579
Now, please take down your hands, both the
hands, and please place them towards Me and

01:31:53.579 --> 01:31:56.539
gradually open your eyes.

01:31:56.539 --> 01:32:06.369
Now, watch Me without thinking.

01:32:06.369 --> 01:32:23.340
Now, please put your left hand towards Me.

01:32:23.340 --> 01:32:33.290
Bend your head and see for yourself if there's
a cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:32:33.290 --> 01:32:36.679
Please see with your right hand.

01:32:36.679 --> 01:32:48.100
Some people get it very close and some far
away but don't put your hand on top of your

01:32:48.100 --> 01:32:49.100
head.

01:32:49.100 --> 01:32:54.930
Just see for yourself if there's a cool breeze
coming out of your head.

01:32:54.930 --> 01:33:04.119
Now, please put your right hand towards Me
and bend your head again and see for yourself

01:33:04.119 --> 01:33:09.530
if there's a cool breeze coming out of your
head.

01:33:09.530 --> 01:33:10.530
Some people get it quite far away.

01:33:10.530 --> 01:33:17.929
Please put again your left hand towards Me
and see for yourself again if there's a cool

01:33:17.929 --> 01:33:24.369
breeze coming out of your head.

01:33:24.369 --> 01:33:37.579
Now raise both your hands towards the sky
like this, push back your head and ask a question,

01:33:37.579 --> 01:33:48.460
"Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy
Ghost?"

01:33:48.460 --> 01:33:49.460
or "Mother, is this the all-pervading power
of God's love?" or "Mother, is this the Paramachaitanya?"

01:33:49.460 --> 01:33:50.460
Any one of these question you ask three times.

01:33:50.460 --> 01:33:51.460
Now, put your hands down.

01:33:51.460 --> 01:33:52.460
You feel very relaxed and there's won't be
any thoughts.

01:33:52.460 --> 01:33:53.460
You can watch Me without thinking.

01:33:53.460 --> 01:33:54.460
All those who have felt cool or hot breeze
on their hands, on their fingertips or out

01:33:54.460 --> 01:33:55.460
of their head, please raise both your hands.

